{"tid":847781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暗殺武器　0.2毫克蓖麻毒素可奪命","createTime":"2018-10-04T12:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T12:25:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be2c9c85ef8fbf03624f1b47d1e77501d14eab30","tid":847781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181004/20514142\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F20514142&d=fph60a7mJUwJE%2BnUXaOkif1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1378ac1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F20514142&h=39ca69b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181004/20514142</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月04日 <br />\n<br />\n暗殺武器　0.2毫克蓖麻毒素可奪命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181004/large/rtr_p_c1555.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181004%2Flarge%2Frtr_p_c1555.jpg&h=ff24c43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國防部長馬蒂斯也收到相信含有劇毒蓖麻的郵件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n<br />\n廣泛存在的蓖麻是少數可以在美國大自然大量取得的毒物，其毒素可以通過進食、呼吸或注射使人體中毒，患者會出現嘔吐、內出血、呼吸困難等反應，嚴重的會器官衰竭而亡。<br />\n<br />\n一般蓖麻種子含有的毒素其實有限，但高純度的蓖麻毒素卻是非同小可，屬生物武器級的毒物，毒性比山埃還要霸道6,000倍，0.2毫克已足以致命，更可怕的是無解藥。<br />\n<br />\n早在冷戰時，蓖麻毒素已被利用為暗殺武器，1978年流亡英國的保加利亞異見作家馬爾可夫（Georgi Markov）突然死亡，法醫驗屍證實他是中了蓖麻毒素，外界相信蘇聯特工是在倫敦街頭，趁馬爾可夫不為意的時候，利用一柄裝有機關的雨傘刺向他的右腿，偽裝成不小心的意外，實際是把高純度蓖麻毒素注入他體內。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n總統、防長、參議員成目標　毒郵件襲華府<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n特朗普被揭助父母逃稅　繼承32億資產"},{"pid":"e97fc11a9cef3e16accaa0de020e8c867d97de84","tid":847781,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:05:53.000Z","msg":"咁侵侵會唔會落台？"},{"pid":"4679b1bce2bc42693d9b712380e652e64026bc3a","tid":847781,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"中國2025"},{"pid":"98ddde7f04f17ddfe7a450e7818cfcd6d315ac0b","tid":847781,"uid":53885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"Breaking bad"},{"pid":"5b166de25c8c49a0bbe989991a2d5df4df70cae0","tid":847781,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"香港大把蓖麻，隨手可得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港獨派會唔會提取蓖麻毒素，上淘寶買部離心機....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0fac87a7f04853ea25e4434620d046510459fb7","tid":847781,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:20:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e367024eb9350c6cf0010186301ce03f3b5ebf2c","tid":847781,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b166de25c8c49a0bbe989991a2d5df4df70cae0","tid":847781,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"香港大把蓖麻，隨手可得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港獨派會唔會提取蓖麻毒素，上淘寶買部離心機....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:22:45.000Z","msg":"我地獨派係唔會用淘寶"},{"pid":"faa09e538ec5b0593cf1b401d313090d90329dba","tid":847781,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf526f4b2ce1b7de5071dbc546c57254114d72e7","tid":847781,"uid":16878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:25:36.000Z","msg":"刺殺金正恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h